-- Toyota Motor to Buy Sanyo Lithium-Ion Batteries From 2011, Yomiuri Reports
-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 2010-09-30T22:06:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/toyota-to-buy-lithium-ion-batteries-from-sanyo-yomiuri-says.html
Toyota Motor Corp. plans to procure
lithium-ion batteries for its hybrid cars from Sanyo Electric
Co. from as early as 2011, the Yomiuri newspaper reported,
citing the carmaker.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
